title: Number of Burger King restaurants in the Asia Pacific region from 2012 to 2013
summary: This grouped bar chart shows SOME LABEL on the Y-axis for 12 different Countrys for 2 groups 2012, and 2013 that are presented on the X-axis.
In Country Australia, 2013 had the highest SOME LABEL 371.0 among the 2 groups and in Philippines, 2012 had the lowest SOME LABEL 29.0.
Among all the Countrys, 2012 had the highest SOME LABEL in Country Australia and lowest SOME LABEL in Country Philippines.
Country Australia and Philippines had the biggest gap of 328.0 between the highest and lowest SOME LABEL found for 2012.
